data.description: Fully furnished duplex for Sale!, Short term rentals permitted. A 2 bed 1 bath apt fully remodeled with outdoor patio & BBQ area, lush landscaping, central ac, separate dining area, private parking. In the 2nd bldg is an updated 1bed 1bath unit, private driveway and small patio. Both units are tastefully furnished and ideal for short term rentals. Close to downtown and the beaches. East of 95 and just West of US1/Federal Hwy. Surrounded by the river, parks, cafe’s and shopping, this property offers an owner multiple options; Rent short term and maximize cash flow, rent furnished annually or redevelop into million dollar townhomes! Favorable zoning for future redevelopment allows 3 stories and 3 Townhomes or 3 apartments and also a mixed use zoning for office and residential.
